This is event display script for HRS

The main program is the executable "program", run it as: ./program

The path of rootfiles and generated plots are set in the def.h file and if you change the paths, remember to do "make" before running the program

The program can be compiled using the Makefile in the directory

The six pads, from left to right, correspond to VDC1, VDC2, Fpp, S2m, prl1 (or preshower), prl2 (or shower) respectively

In the VDC display, the red lines are U wires while blue for V wires

In the Fpp display, the red lines are V wires while blue for U wires

Coordinate system:
		   left -- positive y
		   down -- positive x
